{"tid":1111959,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★唔捱得！【審計報告】僅六成中高齡就業計劃僱員留任逾半年","createTime":"2019-04-17T07:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T11:33:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"01818f9364ea5d1d4304b0784271298e2009678d","tid":1111959,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:13:50.000Z","msg":"勞工處現時推行中高齡就業計劃，審計署今（17日）公布《第七十二號報告書》， 提及當中問題。<br />\n審計署在報告中提到，過去不少合資格僱主未有申請中高齡就業計劃，申請計劃的僱主只佔合資格的總數兩成。<br />\n同時報告又提到，在2017年只有約六成中高齡就業計劃僱員在留任超過半年，相較2015年同期，數字下跌了近16%。審計署建議勞工處檢討計劃成效，並協助在留任方面有困難的中高齡求職人士<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/319074/審計報告-僅六成中高齡就業計劃僱員留任逾半年-兩年跌一成半\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F319074%2F%E5%AF%A9%E8%A8%88%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E5%83%85%E5%85%AD%E6%88%90%E4%B8%AD%E9%AB%98%E9%BD%A1%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%83%B1%E5%93%A1%E7%95%99%E4%BB%BB%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4-%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4%E8%B7%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%88%90%E5%8D%8A&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKMZCnWmYDHHppvVe94ioujI%3D&h=bd3f5180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/319074/審計報告-僅六成中高齡就業計劃僱員留任逾半年-兩年跌一成半</a>"},{"pid":"e1806475ee844659df98318532cd588a939592f6","tid":1111959,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:14:03.000Z","msg":"渣GA"},{"pid":"d7176689c3dbe69e43310bf04d4b9010de503df1","tid":1111959,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:15:56.000Z","msg":"樓豬is one of them"},{"pid":"961977bb2fa5c2537026c7374011c95a2b50fd0e","tid":1111959,"uid":63952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7176689c3dbe69e43310bf04d4b9010de503df1","tid":1111959,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:15:56.000Z","msg":"樓豬is one of them"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"老貓攞綜援<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115c0efdf2a5d7759